string_footer-describe.en: This tool captures a photo from your phone's camera or from an upload and sends it to OpenAI's gpt-4o-mini model for interpretation. I don't store the image, but OpenAI might. See the code and give feedback on GitHub.
string_footer-describe.zh-Hans: 此工具可以从您的手机相机或上传的图片中捕获照片，并将其发送到OpenAI的gpt-4o-mini模型进行解读。我不存储图像，但OpenAI可能会。您可以在GitHub上查看代码并给予反馈。

string_header-title.en: Extract OpenStreetMap tags from an Image
